name: Miss Mehek Taj
greetingText: I'm here to propose you cuz you said i never proposed you
wishText: Life feels unfinished without you, like a story that hasn’t reached its happy ending. With you, everything fits, everything flows, and everything finally makes sense. I don’t want just days with you — I want forever. Will you marry me?the best solution is: Will you be mine forever? ❤️💖
text1: So lets Start it baby you ready? 🥹
textInChatBox: Hey… so, I’ve been thinking. Life’s kind of dull without you around. I like you a lot, and I don’t really want to imagine things without you. So… will you marry me? 🥳 🥳 🥳
text2: Aku tadinya mau chat kamu gitu...
text3: Tapi aku sadar, pengen ngelakuin hal lebih
text4: I realised, I wanted to do something
text5Content: You are special to me Nad 💖
outroText: I hope you liked it! see you nanti sore ya! :D
replayText: Kalau misalnya kamu mau liat lagi, kamu bisa klik text ini ya!
